    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the structured factor evidence and determined that all assessed factors meet or exceed their required credibility levels at MRL 2. The seven assessed factors collectively demonstrate sufficient simulation credibility for the intended use. Non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the scoping rationale documented in the credibility plan. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
